Package: metannoviz
Version: 1.0.2
Title: Process and visualize output from the MetAnnotate pipeline
Description:
    This package facilitates downstream analysis after using
    the MetAnnotate pipeline to scan unassembled metagenome reads from
	environmental metagenome samples for functional genes of interest.
	This package allows for quick exploration and visualization of the
	relative abundances of functional genes compared to a reference taxonomic
	marker gene.
